title: Railworks TS2015 Soldier Summit Route Add-On
description:
The stunning plains and valley passes of Utah make Soldier Summit one of the best loved mountain passes of the western United States. Today, the summit is a popular photo spot for railfans, and the Gilluly loops - a series of horseshoe curves - on the western approach to the summit provide spectacular scenes as heavy freight trains power their way up the pass, a challenging drive for all railroad engineers and one that makes Soldier Summit an epic US rail route. 

NOTE-----> THIS ONLY WORKS ON THE PIRATED VERSION OF TS2015
